ult than loading up a warrior with cobalt and lammys, sit in the middle of orc highway and have a druid heal/regen/DS them while mobs impail themselves.  <br><br>Also players really have to love to nuke stuff they have to truly love it to play a wizard to the top levels.  While you can PL a melee to 50 and get bored, playing a wizard and not loving nukes gets boring FAST <p><b><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=68788'>Oxoxo Xoxox</a></b> Sorcerer<BR><b><a href='http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=57344'>Rubix Stumpyshorts</a></b> lvl 30 Cleric <br>Oxoxo Xoxox lvl 17 Lukreen Eldritch<br>Xoxox Oxoxo lvl 24 Lukreen Mentalist<br>Ouji lvl 10 Lukreen Nightshade<br><A HREF="http://www.mithrilweb.com" target="blank"><img src="http://www.queensidecastle.com/eq/Sorcerersig2.jpg" border="0"></A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujavenado.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Javenado</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/1/02 9:33:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14940.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Transportation</span><hr size=1> At about lvl 14 you will think, man this is hard work,<br>At about 25 you will go nuts,<br>If you havn't quite the wiz yet you'll get an break at 29,<br>35 You'll be going nuts again, <br>41 You will be drinking coffoe 24/7 for 2 weeks in an row <br>and at 48 you will say thats enough and Ebay one.<br><br>We're not an class you can just twink and go out into the world.<br><br>We're an commitment like Marrage, you'll either hate it or love it. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utheperfec