t was fast.<br><br>Start with your basic bugs and bats, no DS even.  Then hit S Ro Orc camps till blue, then move to anything in the desert plus Dervishes.  Use a DS, Regen and C3 + PoTG if you can use those 2 classes.<br><br>After that I did some time in Upper Guk, pulling with Druid, all melee letting the DS do the work.<br><br>Then move to 3 spawn in Lake Rathe.  Use the 60 druid to snare pull singles, burn with Wizard.  This goes pretty fast up to 20, respawn on them is not to bad.  Your mana regen will be faster than mine was, so you may want to substitue a camp with more spawns around the same level range.<br><br>Not sure what level I started, but there is a nice big room in the Tizmak Caves in GD, has 3 spawns plus 2 at entrance to room.  I druid pulled with these and had c2 constant, and could never get all 5 before a repop.  These are good till at least 35 or so.<br><br>After that, I hit gobbies in LOIO at the caves, then think I moved to DL till 51.  Druid fire DeBuff will make a world of difference to.<br><br>Those are just a few areas I hit.  Less that 12 days played and I'm 53 now.  Don't use Druid or Enchanter anymore, friend hocked his account =(  Been quadding at Undead ruins in BW&lt; but that getting a lot of light blue lately, guess it's Raptor time, /yeck. <p>Sildiven Azuenden<BR>52nd Wizard of Agnostic!<BR><BR>Sollwin Lifestar <BR>58th Templar Of Bristlebane<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sepp>Sepp</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/1/02 11:45:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=14940.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=